CITY EQUITY CO. v. JONES et al. (Supreme Court, Appellate Division, Second Department. December 30, 1909.) Appeal from Special Term, Richmond County. Action by the City Equity Company against Minnie E. Jones and others. Judgment for plaintiff, and defendants,' except Mary Elizabeth Housman, appeal. Affirmed.

Argued before WOODWARD. JENKS, BURR, THOMAS, and RICH.. JJ.

*440H. J. McCormick, for appellants. Benjamin N. Cardozo (Harold Swain and Alfred G. Reeves, on the brief), for respondent. PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed, with costs, upon the authority of City Equity Co. v. Elm Park Realty Co. (decided herewith) 120 N. Y. Supp. 437.
